        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName>Down Beckenham</placeName>
                    <date>Ap. 7.</date>
                    <salute>Dear D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Günther</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>We should be so glad if you would come to us on Saturday next &amp; stay over the Sunday with us— In case we may hope to see you I wd recommend the 4.12 train from Charing Cross to Orpington which is the one we generally meet—</p>
<p>With M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Darwin’s kind regards very truly yours | Emma Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

            
            
        </div>

        

        

